info.author: Horacio Duran
info.description:
Introduction
============

- Code repository: https://svn.plone.org/svn/collective/plonetheme.bronzecube
- Questions and comments to hduran "at" machinalis [dot] com
- Report bugs by mail for now

-- INSTALL

Add plonetheme.bronzecube to the list of eggs to install, e.g.:

    [buildout]
    ...
    eggs =
       ...
       plonetheme.bronzecube

    [instance]
    ...
    eggs =
        ...
        plonetheme.bronzecube

With portal_quickinstaller install


Changelog
=========

1.0dev (unreleased)
-------------------

- Initial release
